item.title: GNOME.org revamp
item.description: After lots of stops and starts over the last few years, which really isn’t worth recapping, the GNOME web team is moving forward with a new www.gnome.org. After lots of chatter on the gnome-web mailing lists the last couple months, Lucas organized a meeting, a set of tasks to be completed, and the timeline. Personally, I’m helping with the content team – do we have the right pages for the new www.
